Package: simpipe
Type: Package
Title: A standard pipeline of simulating single-cell RNA sequencing data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Hongrui", "Duo", role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "Duohongrui@cqnu.edu.cn",
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8683-015X")),
      person("Bo", "Li", role = c("aut"),
      email = "libo@cqnu.edu.cn",
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9944-0003")))
Maintainer: Hongrui Duo <duohongrui@cqnu.edu.cn>
Description: The series steps of estimating parameters from real data, simulating
    scRNA-seq datasets and evaluating the simulated data with real data are packaged
    in this project. The prevalent methods of simulating scRNA-seq datasets are 
    involved in this project and we will still add new important methods in the future.
